      "content": "Wait, \"goblin hunter\"? What the hell are you talking about? Just stick to the technical logs. Also, why did you say you updated the routing table locally? I didn't authorize any config changes to the gateway. Revert the changes and send me the exact timestamp of when that \"update\" occurred.",
